Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.52,0:08:08.44,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{So you left a small child all alone?}¿Así que dejaste a una pequeña niña sola?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.23,0:08:11.40,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{The girl can take care of herself now.}Ella puede cuidarse sola ahora.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.36,0:08:14.70,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{Her troubles stem from me anyway.}Sus problemas provienen de mí de todos modos.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.20,0:08:17.83,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{Besides, I left her a note.}Además, le dejé una nota.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.33,0:08:19.62,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{That note...}Esa nota...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.70,0:08:22.29,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{A neighborhood cat took off with it.}Un gato del vecindario se la llevó.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.37,0:08:23.50,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{What!}¡¿Cómo dices?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.25,0:08:25.38,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{I saw it happen.}Lo que escuchas.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.46,0:08:26.92,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{Oh, no...}No puede ser{Qué problema}...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.63,0:08:29.63,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{Now it'll look like I left without a word...}Ahora pensará que me fui sin despedirme...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.46,0:08:34.30,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{Well, I'll return once I've reached my goal, so it shouldn't be a problem.}Bueno, regresaré una vez que cumpla mi objetivo, así que no debería haber problema.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.89,0:08:38.64,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{And this goal, is to find Homura's real mother, yeas?}Y este objetivo, es encontrar a la madre de Homura, ¿cierto?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.43,0:08:42.02,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{You really do know everything, don't you?}Realmente lo sabes todo, ¿no?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.60,0:08:44.23,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{I am the time oracle.}Soy el Oráculo del Tiempo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.98,0:08:49.32,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{Homura needs a mother. Her real mother.}Homura necesita una madre. Su verdadera madre.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.57,0:08:52.19,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{I want you to tell me where she is.}Quiero que me digas dónde está.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.49,0:08:55.11,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{I will see for you.}Dame un momento.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.82,0:08:58.49,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{The location of Homura's mother...}La localización de la madre de Homura...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.54,0:09:02.41,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{..Kurenai Kogetsu.}...Kurenai Kogetsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.09,0:09:12.30,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{I finally found you, Kurenai Kogetsu.}Por fin te encuentro, Kurenai Kogetsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.88,0:09:17.34,EZ Subs Test,,0,0,0,,{Planet \NSun Jewel,\N five years \Nago.}{Planeta Sun Jewel, hace 5 años.}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.88,0:09:14.30,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{Who are you...?}¿Quién eres tú...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.38,0:09:15.93,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{I am Valkyrie.}Soy Valkyrie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.43,0:09:18.76,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{And you are Homura's mother, I presume?}Y supongo que tú eres la madre de Homura.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.85,0:09:20.35,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,¿Homura?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.23,0:09:27.31,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{I see... \NShe's still alive...}Ya veo... Aún está bien...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.90,0:09:30.77,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{I can see they put you through a lot.}Puedo ver que has pasado por mucho.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.86,0:09:34.40,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{This place is ruled by the lecherous Baron Mordo.}Este lugar está gobernado por el lascivo Baron Mordo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.49,0:09:36.11,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{It's all right now.}Todo estará bien ahora.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.20,0:09:38.66,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{I'm going to take you back to Homura.}Te llevaré de regreso con Homura.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.16,0:09:41.08,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{What are you talking about?}¿De qué estás hablando?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.95,0:09:46.42,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{As long as I have this collar, I'm as good as a slave.}Mientras tenga este collar, no soy más que una esclava.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.50,0:09:49.79,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{That's why, I have a man who can remove it.}Es por eso que encontré a alguien que te lo puede quitar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.59,0:09:53.42,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{Sure, with my Steal ability,}Seguro, con mi habilidad Steal,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.51,0:09:55.13,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{taking that collar'll be a piece of cake.}quitarte ese collar será pan comido.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.72,0:09:57.68,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{But I don't wanna get mixed up in your problems.}Pero no quiero que me metas en tus asuntos.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.76,0:09:59.47,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{This is the thief Paul.}Este es el ladrón Paul.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.97,0:10:01.68,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{Ex-thief, teacher.}Ex-ladrón, maestra.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.76,0:10:04.60,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{If you can remove collars, \Nwhy don't you remove your own?}Si puedes remover los collares, ¿por qué no lo haces con el tuyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.68,0:10:06.35,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{I'm so glad you asked.}Me alegra que preguntes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.44,0:10:09.94,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{You know we mine the metal \Nthat gets sent to Baron Mordo.}Tú sabes que extraemos el mineral que es enviado a Baron Mordo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.02,0:10:13.98,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{But occasionally, we get \Nsome rare ore that doesn't get sent away.}Pero de vez en cuando, obtenemos algún mineral raro que no se puede enviar.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.57,0:10:19.41,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{And that ore is a mass of highly condensed Ether,\Ncommonly known as "celestial tears".}Y ese mineral, es una masa de Ether altamente concentrada, conocido como "Lágrimas celestiales".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.49,0:10:20.87,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{The Lacrima.}La Lágrima.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.95,0:10:23.66,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{You can sell those for a pretty high price.}Puedes verderlos por un precio bastante alto.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.29,0:10:28.12,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{But never mind him. We're going home, together.}No le hagas caso. Nos irémos a casa, juntas.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.62,0:10:30.00,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{Homura is waiting.}Homura está esperando.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.59,0:10:34.63,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{I appreciate your offer, but...}Aprecio tu oferta, pero...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.21,0:10:36.63,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{I cannot.}No puedo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.93,0:10:40.43,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{I have a debt to pay.}Tengo una deuda que pagar.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.30,0:10:44.77,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{I left home to make money. I dreamed of striking it rich...}Dejé  mi hogar para hacer dinero. Soñé con hacerme rica...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.85,0:10:47.60,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{But ended up with a huge debt\N in the wealthy sector casinos.}Pero terminé con una gran deuda en los casinos del sector rico.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.35,0:10:50.98,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{If I don't pay it back, then Homura...!}¡Si no lo devuelvo, entonces Homura...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.48,0:10:53.02,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{They're sure to go after her!}¡Seguro irán tras ella!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.86,0:10:55.99,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{That's why...}Por eso...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.57,0:10:59.95,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{I can't run away. No matter how much I may want to.}No puedo huir. No importa cuánto desee volver.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.03,0:11:02.20,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{Then there's a simple solution to that problem.}En ese caso, hay una solución simple para este problema.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.78,0:11:05.87,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{Paul, put Kurenai's collar on my neck.}Paul, pon el collar de Kurenai en mi cuello.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.95,0:11:06.58,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{What?}¡¿Qué?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.08,0:11:09.92,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{I will earn the money to pay back your debt.}Ganaré el dinero para pagar tu deuda.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.00,0:11:12.50,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{That's... I can't let you-!!}¡Eso...! ¡De ninguna manera!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.17,0:11:15.34,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{I know how the system works here.}Sé como funciona el sistema aquí.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.42,0:11:18.72,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{Let me handle this. Combat is my specialty.}Déjame manejar esto. El combate es mi especialidad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.80,0:11:20.55,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{But... But, teacher...}P-Pero, maestra...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.63,0:11:25.22,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{Returning without achieving my goal would be a disgrace to the Demon King's Four Shining Stars.}Regresar sin cumplir mi objetivo, sería una vergüenza como una de las  Cuatro Estrellas Brillantes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.06,0:11:27.27,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{Please, Kurenai.}Te lo pido, Kurenai.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.77,0:11:30.19,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{This is why I came here.}Esto es por lo que vine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.69,0:11:32.44,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{Go back to Homura.}Regresa con Homura.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.94,0:11:39.99,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{I will remember your kindness for the rest of my life...}Recordaré tu amabilidad por el resto de mi vida...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.07,0:11:41.66,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{Lady Valkyrie...}Señora Valkyrie...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.91,0:11:49.33,EZ Subs Test,,0,0,0,,{Two\N years\N later}{Dos años después.}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.95,0:11:46.83,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{Pip!}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.08,0:11:54.92,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{A woman's "life" must not be very long, eh teacher?}La vida de una mujer no debe ser muy larga. ¿No, profesora?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.00,0:11:56.38,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{What are you talking about?}¿De qué estás hablando?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.46,0:11:58.59,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{Oh, some new intel I recently picked up.}Algo de información nueva que obtuve recientementel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.47,0:12:03.05,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{That Kurenai woman.\N The one teacher gave up her freedom for.}Esa mujer, Kurenai. Aquella por la que usted renunció a su libertad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.64,0:12:06.56,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{Apparently, she took up with Baron Mordo,}Parecer ser que ella se fue con Baron Mordo
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.64,0:12:08.77,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{ended up as his legal wife.}y se convirtió en su esposa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.35,0:12:11.89,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{She didn't go back to Homura?!}¡¿Ella no regresó con Homura'!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.39,0:12:14.94,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{ Next time I will drag her home if I have to!}¡La próxima vez la arrastraré a casa si es necesario!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.52,0:12:16.73,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{Yeah, well...}Sí, bueno...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.40,0:12:20.40,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{After that, she assassinated Baron Mordo,}Después de eso, ella asesinó a Baron Mordo,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.49,0:12:22.99,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{seized power over the entire planet,}tomó el poder del planeta entero
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.07,0:12:26.28,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{and now she's calling herself Madame Kurenai.}y ahora se llama así misma Madame Kurenai.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.66,0:12:29.75,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{What happened to her?!}¿Qué fue lo que le pasó?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.08,0:12:33.79,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{Nothing happened. She was always that way.}No le pasó nada, siempre fue de esa manera.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.87,0:12:37.29,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{Oh, but don't start \Ndistrusting all humans over this, teacher.}¡Ah! Pero no empieces a desconfiar de todos los humanos después de esto, maestra.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.09,0:12:38.63,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{Tch...}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.21,0:12:43.01,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{I won't. Being human or android has nothing to do with making evil choices.}Ya lo sé. Ser humano o un androide no tiene nada que ver con tomar malas decisiones.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.51,0:12:45.55,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{Paul! Take off my collar!}¡Paul! ¡Deshazte de mi collar!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.64,0:12:47.60,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{I'm going to set that woman straight!}¡Voy a poner a esa mujer en su lugar!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.68,0:12:48.47,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{Yes!}¡Sí!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.77,0:12:54.10,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{What was that...?}¿Qué pasa...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.77,0:12:56.65,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{It came from the mining site!}¡Viene del área minera!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.82,0:13:07.62,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{A swarm of Stones!?}¡¿Un enjambre de Stones?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.45,0:13:13.83,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{Lady Valkyrie! It's terrible!}¡Lady Valkyrie! ¡Es terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.91,0:13:16.75,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{That woman who took over after Baron Mordo...}Esa mujer que tomó control después de Mordo...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.42,0:13:19.96,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{She says we have to mine more metal,}¡Dijo que tenemos que minar más material,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.05,0:13:24.26,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{so she agitated \Nall the Stones in the mine, and now this!}por lo que provocó a todos los Stones en la mina y esto pasó!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.34,0:13:27.72,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,¡Kurenai!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.80,0:13:30.56,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{At this rate, they'll stampede right into the residential district!}¡A este ritmo, la estampida llegará al distrito residencial!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.64,0:13:32.77,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{Set up a line of defense!}¡Hagan una línea de defensa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.85,0:13:34.98,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{We must keep them here at all costs!}¡Debemos mantenerlos aquí a cualquier costo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.65,0:13:39.98,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{All of you go help defend the residential district!}¡Todos ustedes, ayuden a proteger el distrito residencial!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.07,0:13:41.48,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{T-Teacher, you?!}¡¿M-Maestra...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.57,0:13:43.07,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{I will keep them here!}¡No los dejaré pasar!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.90,0:13:46.74,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{This is my responsibility! I released that woman!}¡Es mi responsabilidad! ¡Yo liberé a esa mujer!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.24,0:13:48.95,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{I'll deal with this myself!}¡Me encargaré de esto yo misma!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.03,0:13:51.83,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{That's absurd! There's too many of them!}¡Eso es absurdo! ¡Son demasiados!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.91,0:13:52.79,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{Go!}¡Vayan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.45,0:13:55.66,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{Valkyrie Armament System Online!}¡Sistema Armamento Valquiria, en línea!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.17,0:13:57.75,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,¡Odin Strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.83,0:14:01.38,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{My power was once called the Sword of Edens!}¡Mi poder fue llamado una vez la espada de Edens!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.46,0:14:02.46,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{Now you'll see why!}¡Les mostraré por qué!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.03,0:14:29.45,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{Oooh! Look!}¡Miren!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.53,0:14:32.24,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{All this metal in just one fight!}¡Todo este mineral en una sola batalla!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.83,0:14:35.79,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{You prisoners can do it if you put your minds to it!}¡Los prisioneros pueden hacerlo si se lo proponen!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.87,0:14:37.21,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{Ahahahaha!}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.26,0:15:28.67,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{I love my mentor.}Te quiero mucho, maestra.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.59,0:15:34.01,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{Come to think of it...}Pensándolo bien...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.81,0:15:37.43,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{I never did say it, did I?}Nunca se lo dije, ¿cierto?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.56,0:15:42.27,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{I...}Yo también..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.53,0:15:49.90,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{I love you, too.}Yo también te quiero.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.53,0:15:58.41,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{T-Teacher...}M-Maestra...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.50,0:16:01.37,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{It's not true...}Esto no es cierto...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.37,0:16:05.17,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{This... cannot... be true...}Esto no puede ser real...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.38,0:16:13.47,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{Lady Valkyrie...}La señora Valkyrie...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.55,0:16:15.43,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{In order to protect us at that time...}con el fin de protegernos...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.43,0:16:17.85,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{That's how she died.}dio su vida.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.93,0:16:21.27,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{Teacher...}Maestra...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.90,0:16:26.82,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{I've been... looking for you... all this time.}Te he buscado... todo este tiempo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.69,0:16:29.74,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{All this time...}Todo el tiempo...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.70,0:16:34.24,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{I've missed you so much, but...}Te extraño demasiado, pero...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.99,0:16:37.49,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{And this is how it ends...?!}¡¿Así es como acabará?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.24,0:16:41.66,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{Teacher! It is I! Homura!}¡Maestra! ¡Soy yo! ¡Homura!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.75,0:16:43.42,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{Answer me, I beg of you!}¡Respóndeme! ¡Te lo ruego!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.42,0:16:45.63,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{Teacher!}¡Maestra!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.75,0:16:51.22,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{Please! You must awaken!}¡Por favor! ¡Debes despertar!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.13,0:16:55.55,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{Of course! Weisz can fix her!}¡Claro! ¡Weisz puede arreglarla!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.14,0:16:57.60,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{Or, or Sister could!}¡O.. O quizás Sister podría!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.68,0:17:02.02,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{...When an android's core stops...}Cuando el núcleo de un androide se detiene...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.52,0:17:05.40,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{It means the same thing... as death for a human...}significa lo mismo que... la muerta para los humanos.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.48,0:17:08.82,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{N-Noooo...}¡N-No...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.40,0:17:14.82,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{No...\NI'll never see my mentor again!}¡No puede ser...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.42,0:17:28.67,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{Where's Homura?}¿Dónde está Homura?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.75,0:17:31.46,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{She hasn't left Miss Valkyrie's side.}Ella no se ha ido del lado de la señora Valkyrie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.17,0:17:34.59,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{We'll never get the Four Shining Stars together now.}Ahora nunca podremos reunir a las Cuatro Estrellas Brillantes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.09,0:17:37.18,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{I suppose that is the case.}Supongo que así es.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.26,0:17:40.64,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{Who would've thought that girl was Homura?}Quién hubiera pensado que esa chica era Homura.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.27,0:17:44.18,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{We have held Lady Valkyrie \Nin the highest respect since that day.}Hemos mantenido un gran respeto por la señora Valkyrie desde ese día.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.27,0:17:46.15,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{We even call ourselves Valkyrie's army.}Incluso nos llamamos el ejército de Valkyrie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.90,0:17:50.15,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{If you respect her so much, why did you leave her body exposed to the elements?}Si la respetan tanto, ¿por qué dejaron su cuerpo expuesto a la intemperie?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.23,0:17:52.11,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{It's not like that!}¡No es lo que crees!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.19,0:17:54.36,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{She's our beacon!}¡Ella es nuestro símbolo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.45,0:17:56.20,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{It's because of Lady Valkyrie,}¡Es por la señora Valkyrie
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.28,0:17:57.95,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{that we've been able to keep going for so long!}que hemos podido continuar durante tanto tiempo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.45,0:18:01.91,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{And besides, till the day that Homura came to find her,}Además, desde el día que Homura vino a buscarla,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.99,0:18:03.95,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{we felt that we shouldn't touch her.}sentimos que no debíamos tocarla.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.04,0:18:05.29,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{I see.}Ya veo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.79,0:18:11.00,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{We've been preparing the rebellion against Madame Kurenai for a long time.}Hemos estado preparándonos para la rebelión contra Madame Kurenai durante mucho tiempo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.09,0:18:12.59,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{You might call us the resistance.}Puedes llamarnos la resitencia.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.67,0:18:14.55,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{Resistance?}¿Resistencia?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.13,0:18:17.01,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{And now that Homura has come here,}Y ahora que Homura ha llegado,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.09,0:18:19.22,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{the last piece is in place.}la última pieza está en su lugar.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.97,0:18:21.68,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{You'll fight with us, right?}Lucharán con nosotros, ¿cierto?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.43,0:18:29.10,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{Right now, I think I'd rather let her grieve in peace.}Por ahora, creo que prefiero dejarla llorar en paz.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.44,0:18:36.86,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{Your mentor really is awesome.}Tu maestra es realmente increíble.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.45,0:18:39.49,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{She's strong, and she's cool.}Es fuerte y genial.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.41,0:18:42.49,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{She fought to protect humans.}Luchó para proteger a los humanos.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.99,0:18:44.12,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{She was brave, too.}También fue muy valiente.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.00,0:18:47.16,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{She had a kind heart.}Ella tenía un buen corazón.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.17,0:18:50.79,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{I'm sure she would have made a great friend.}Estoy seguro que hubiera sido una gran amiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.05,0:18:56.09,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,Shiki...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.93,0:18:59.26,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{I do not know...}No sé...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.76,0:19:02.55,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{If I can recover from this.}si pueda recuperarme de esto.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.52,0:19:08.27,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{That's okay. For now, anyway.}Eso está bien. Por ahora, de todos modos.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.77,0:19:10.73,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.44,0:19:16.11,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{I will never be able to...}Nunca seré capaz de...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.40,0:19:19.53,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{Back when my grandpa died,}Cuando mi abuelo murió,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.03,0:19:22.03,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{it hit me really hard, too.}también me dolió demasiado.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.12,0:19:26.87,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{But... I had Michael\N and the townspeople. I had my friends.}Pero... tenía a Michael y a la gente de la ciudad. Tenía a mis amigos.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.66,0:19:27.77,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{So I managed to keep moving forward.}Así que me las arreglé para seguir adelante.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.78,0:19:28.83,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{So I managed to keep pressing on.}Para seguir intentándolo{???}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.25,0:19:34.34,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{You have friends, too, Homura.}También tienes amigos, Homura.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.42,0:19:39.38,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{So I know you can keep pressing on, too.}Así que también... puedes seguir intentándolo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.44,0:19:52.90,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,Oculus Kurenai.{Ojo Carmesí}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.56,0:19:57.15,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{Locking on to entire Labor district.\N Entering radiation sequence.}Bloqueando el distrito laboral.\NEntrando en la secuencia de radiación.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.65,0:19:59.32,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{Beginning system check.}Iniciando sistema de chequeo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.40,0:20:01.99,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{You can't be serious!}¡¿Estás hablando en serio?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.07,0:20:04.87,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{There are tens of thousands people down there!}¡Hay decenas de miles de personas ahí abajo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.95,0:20:07.08,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{They aren't making me any money.}Ellos no me están haciendo ganar dinero.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.16,0:20:11.83,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{And worse than that, they worship that piece of trash as if she were a saint!}¡Y peor que eso, adoran a ese pedazo de basura como si fuera una santa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.92,0:20:14.88,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{Those pieces of garbage \Nwill pay for rebelling against me!}¡Esos pedazos de basura, pagarán por rebelarse contra mí!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.59,0:20:16.63,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{Wasn't it Valkyrie,}¡¿No fue Valkyrie...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.71,0:20:19.30,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{the one that saved you from the Labor district?!}la que te liberó del distrito laboral?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.38,0:20:21.76,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{Not at all!}¡Para nada!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.84,0:20:24.26,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{I merely allowed her to be useful.}Simplemente le permití serme de utilidad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.18,0:20:28.31,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{I rose to greatness by my own power.}Alcancé a la grandeza por mis propios medios.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.39,0:20:31.35,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{I have done nothing \Nto earn me the spite of that rabble!}¡No he hecho nada para ganarme el desprecio de esa chusma{gentuza}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.14,0:20:33.48,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{Oh, yes. It was Valkyrie,}De hecho, fue Valkyrie
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.56,0:20:36.61,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{the one that requested me to return to my daughter.}la que me pidió que regresara con mi hija.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.69,0:20:38.15,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{Ufufu...}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.07,0:20:41.36,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{As if I hadn't ditched the \Ngirl to come here in the first place!}¡Como si no la hubiera abandonado para venir aquí{acá en primer lugar}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.45,0:20:43.07,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{What was she thinking?}¿Qué diablos estaba pensando?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.91,0:20:46.95,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{Ahahahahaha~!}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.00,0:20:55.63,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{Which one of you is Madame Kurenai?!}¡¿Quién de ustedes es Madame Kurenai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.29,0:20:58.88,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{-Who goes there?!\N-Is it you?!}-¡¿Qué haces aquí?!\N-¡¿Eres tú?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.84,0:21:02.51,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{I'm taking you to see Homura.}Voy a llevarte donde Homura.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.01,0:21:05.59,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{Because that was Valkyrie's wish.}Porque eso era lo que Valkyrie quería.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.18,0:21:09.01,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{Homura? No way, she's on this planet?}¿Homura? De ninguna manera, ¿está en este planeta?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.02,0:21:11.98,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{Is that girl angry?}¿Acaso está enojada?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.06,0:21:15.02,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{Or is she crying because she was abandoned?}¿O estará llorando porque fue abandonada?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.10,0:21:17.77,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{Homura will decide what we do with you.}Homura decidirá lo que haremos contigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.86,0:21:19.57,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{I'm terribly sorry.}Lo lamento mucho.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.65,0:21:24.03,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{I have absolutely zero interest in my daughter.}No tengo ni una pizca de interés en mi hija.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.74,0:21:31.08,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{Wha- The floor is collapsing!}¡El piso está colapsando!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.12,0:21:33.50,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{You're coming with me.}Tú vienes conmigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.58,0:21:36.33,EZ Subs,,0,0,0,,{After I beat the crap out of you.}Después de que te de una paliza.
